<feed xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:openSearch="https://a9.com/-/spec/opensearch/1.1/" xmlns:batch="https://schemas.google.com/gdata/batch" xmlns:gd="https://schemas.google.com/g/2005" xmlns:gs="https://schemas.google.com/spreadsheets/2006" xmlns:thr="https://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0" xmlns:sites="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008" xmlns:dc="https://purl.org/dc/terms" xmlns:gAcl="https://schemas.google.com/acl/2007"><id>https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan</id><updated>2022-08-17T06:59:21.536Z</updated><title>Posts of F - Khuyển Thủ Dạ</title><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan" /><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/g/2005#feed" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan" /><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/g/2005#post" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan" /><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/g/2005#batch" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/batch" /><link rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan?parent=1625853613955352795&amp;kind=announcement" /><generator version="1" uri="https://sites.google.com">Google Sites</generator><openSearch:startIndex>1</openSearch:startIndex><entry gd:etag="&quot;YD0peyY.&quot;"><id>https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/941545399420281824</id><published>2013-06-09T04:54:07.905Z</published><updated>2013-06-10T16:05:47.511Z</updated><app:edited xmlns:app="https://www.w3.org/2007/app">2013-06-10T16:05:47.509Z</app:edited><category scheme="https://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind" term="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#announcement" label="announcement" /><title>44 Nhân di tử kim mãn doanh</title><content type="xhtml"><div xmlns="https://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><div class="sites-layout-name-two-column-hf sites-layout-vbox"><div class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-header"><div dir="ltr"><div align="center">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none">
 <tbody><tr>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">1</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">2</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">3</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">4</font></p>
  </td>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">人遺子，金滿籯；</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">我教子，惟一經。</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">勤有功，戲無益；</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">戒之哉，宜勉力。</span></font></p>
  </td>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Nhân di tử, kim mãn doanh; </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Ngã giáo tử, duy nhất kinh. </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Cần hữu công, hí vô ích; </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><font face="times new roman, serif">Giới chi tai, nghi miễn lực. </font></font></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</tbody></table>

</div></div></div><table cellspacing="0" class="sites-layout-hbox"><tbody><tr><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-1"><div dir="ltr"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4"><ol><li>Người ta để lại cho con đầy rương vàng </li><li>Ta dạy con chỉ có một bộ sách. </li><li>Siêng thì có công, ham chơi thì vô ích </li><li>Khuyên răn trò gắng sức học. </li></ol></font><hr /><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Người ta để lại cho con vàng rồng đầy rương; ta dạy cho con chỉ một bộ sách. Siêng thì có công, ham chơi thì không có ích. Khuyên răn trò gắng sức học.</font></div></td><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-2 sites-layout-empty-tile"><div dir="ltr"><br /></div></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-footer sites-layout-empty-tile"><div dir="ltr"><br /></div></div></div></div></content><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#parent" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/1625853613955352795" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://sites.google.com/site/cohanvan/Tu-hoc/can-ban/tam-tu-kinh/khuyen-thu-da/44nhanditukimmandoanh" /><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#revision" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/revision/site/cohanvan/941545399420281824" /><link rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/941545399420281824" /><link rel="edit" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/941545399420281824" /><author><name>Lỗ Bình Sơn</name><email>lobinhson@gmail.com</email></author><sites:pageName>44nhanditukimmandoanh</sites:pageName><sites:revision>1</sites:revision></entry><entry gd:etag="&quot;YD0peyY.&quot;"><id>https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/7936408592821126203</id><published>2013-06-09T04:52:12.769Z</published><updated>2013-06-09T04:52:12.772Z</updated><app:edited xmlns:app="https://www.w3.org/2007/app">2013-06-09T04:52:12.766Z</app:edited><category scheme="https://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind" term="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#announcement" label="announcement" /><title>43 Ấu nhi học tráng nhi hành</title><content type="xhtml"><div xmlns="https://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><div class="sites-layout-name-two-column-hf sites-layout-vbox"><div class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-header"><div dir="ltr"><div align="center">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none">
 <tbody><tr>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">1</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">2</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">3</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">4</font></p>
  </td>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">幼而學，壯而行；</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">上致君，下澤民。</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">揚名聲，顯父母；</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">光于前，裕于后。</span></font></p>
  </td>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Ấu nhi học, tráng nhi hành; </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Thượng trí quân, hạ trạch dân. </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Dương danh thanh, hiển phụ mẫu; </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><font face="times new roman, serif">Quang ư tiền, dụ ư hậu. </font></font></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</tbody></table>

</div></div></div><table cellspacing="0" class="sites-layout-hbox"><tbody><tr><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-1"><div dir="ltr"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4"><ol><li>Nhỏ thì học, lớn lên thì làm </li><li>Trên giúp vua, dưới làm ích cho dân </li><li>Tiếng tăm vang dội, cha mẹ vẻ vang </li><li>Rạng ngời về đời trước, truyền lại tới đời sau. </li></ol></font><hr /><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Lúc trẻ thì học, lúc lớn thì hành; trên giúp nên cho vua, dưới ra ơn cho dân, tiếng tăm vang vội, làm vẻ vang cha mẹ. Rạng ngời về đời trước, truyền lại tới đời sau.</font></div></td><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-2 sites-layout-empty-tile"><div dir="ltr"><br /></div></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-footer sites-layout-empty-tile"><div dir="ltr"><br /></div></div></div></div></content><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#parent" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/1625853613955352795" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://sites.google.com/site/cohanvan/Tu-hoc/can-ban/tam-tu-kinh/khuyen-thu-da/43aunhihoctrangnhihanh" /><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#revision" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/revision/site/cohanvan/7936408592821126203" /><link rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/7936408592821126203" /><link rel="edit" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/7936408592821126203" /><author><name>Lỗ Bình Sơn</name><email>lobinhson@gmail.com</email></author><sites:pageName>43aunhihoctrangnhihanh</sites:pageName><sites:revision>1</sites:revision></entry><entry gd:etag="&quot;YD0peyY.&quot;"><id>https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/1027516934603012447</id><published>2013-06-09T04:50:10.836Z</published><updated>2013-06-09T04:50:10.840Z</updated><app:edited xmlns:app="https://www.w3.org/2007/app">2013-06-09T04:50:10.833Z</app:edited><category scheme="https://schemas.google.com/g/2005#kind" term="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#announcement" label="announcement" /><title>42 Khuyển thủ dạ kê ti thần</title><content type="xhtml"><div xmlns="https://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><div class="sites-layout-name-two-column-hf sites-layout-vbox"><div class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-header"><div dir="ltr"><div align="center">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none">
 <tbody><tr>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">1</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">2</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">3</font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5">4</font></p>
  </td>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">犬守夜，雞司晨；</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">苟不學，曷為人？</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">蠶吐絲，蜂釀蜜；</span></font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><span lang="ZH-CN">人不學，不如物。</span></font></p>
  </td>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Khuyển thủ dạ, kê ti thần; </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Cẩu bất học, hạt vi nhân? </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Tàm thổ ti, phong nhưỡng mật; </font></p>
  <p><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><font face="times new roman, serif">Nhân bất học, bất như vật. </font></font></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</tbody></table>

</div></div></div><table cellspacing="0" class="sites-layout-hbox"><tbody><tr><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-1"><div dir="ltr"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4"><ol><li>Chó giữa nhà ban đêm, gà coi gáy buổi sáng. </li><li>Nếu không học sao đáng làm người? </li><li>Con tằm nhả tơ, con ông làm mật </li><li>Người mà không học chẳng bằng con vật. </li></ol></font><hr /><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Con chó giữ nhà ban đêm, con gà coi gáy buổi sáng, nếu trò chẳng học sao đáng làm người? Con tằm nhả tơ, con ông gây mật, người ta mà chẳng học chẳng bằng giống vật.</font></div></td><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-2 sites-layout-empty-tile"><div dir="ltr"><br /></div></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-footer sites-layout-empty-tile"><div dir="ltr"><br /></div></div></div></div></content><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#parent" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/1625853613955352795" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://sites.google.com/site/cohanvan/Tu-hoc/can-ban/tam-tu-kinh/khuyen-thu-da/42khuyenthudaketithan" /><link rel="https://schemas.google.com/sites/2008#revision" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/revision/site/cohanvan/1027516934603012447" /><link rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/1027516934603012447" /><link rel="edit" type="application/atom+xml" href="https://sites.google.com/feeds/content/site/cohanvan/1027516934603012447" /><author><name>Lỗ Bình Sơn</name><email>lobinhson@gmail.com</email></author><sites:pageName>42khuyenthudaketithan</sites:pageName><sites:revision>1</sites:revision></entry></feed>
